In [187]:
import pandas as pd
df = pd.read_csv("D:\DESKTOP\Latest Covid-19 India Status.csv")
group_size = [sum(df.Deaths), sum(df.Active), sum(df.Discharged)]
group_labels = ["Deaths\n"+str(sum(df.Deaths)),
                "Active\n"+str(sum(df.Active)),
                "Dishcarged\n"+str(sum(df.Discharged))]
custom_colors = ["skyblue", "yellowgreen", 'tomato']
plt.figure(figsize=(10,10))
plt.pie(group_size, labels=group_labels, colors=custom_colors)
plt.rc('font', size=20)
plt.title("Total Deaths, Active, and Discharged Cases", fontsize=20)
plt.show()
